title: Jim Garrison Discusses Jack Ruby
description:
From a longer talk from one of Jim Garrison's speaking tours, the content of which is repeated here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P5zeuEm4Yzg This short section on Jack Ruby was the only part not repeated so I'm posting it here.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
